{"tid":213200,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇啲人背住女朋友去叫雞","createTime":"2017-04-23T03:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T04:11:46.000Z","uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ee052665c8c1cc57a7d8706f071436656fae63","tid":213200,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"最近知道左幾個朋友（唔熟）有女朋友 <br />\n但仲要去叫雞 大陸雞泰國雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想知佢地女朋友知道會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2113a06382994cc79fc40fce0f8e0c3ffd9f8a0","tid":213200,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"各取所需"},{"pid":"6613472ebdee5499b36cb83efa9f7c961e735ec5","tid":213200,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各取所需</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各取所需 係女朋友知道但容許<br />\n但依家係女朋友唔知<br />\n仲要個男人人前對個女朋友係好好<br />\n但就背住佢叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71419a85e1a31b628fe6706b7efa83835710e51f","tid":213200,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"一齊浸豬籠開心"},{"pid":"a5e467ecaeabb5f833df8717e16e69acf917e992","tid":213200,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>各取所需</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各取所需 係女朋友知道但容許<br />\n但依家係女朋友唔知<br />\n仲要個男人人前對個女朋友係好好<br />\n但就背住佢叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可以點？<br />\n唔抵得人地又有女又去叫雞咩？<br />\n我夠識人有女仲叫雞喇<br />\n佢地一定話自己冇錯架啵"},{"pid":"7bccab1afae6029a0672ecdc14192c81bf5343f4","tid":213200,"uid":78679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"可以點睇<br />\nD 人永遠都係講到男人偷食無錯<br />\n女人應該扮唔知 男人識番屋企就得 <br />\n但女人偷食就十惡不赦 <br />\n根本所有男人都係狗"},{"pid":"6bcc01fc5ad98d4ce293bb636bb9a84eddbacc80","tid":213200,"uid":56368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以點睇<br />\nD 人永遠都係講到男人偷食無錯<br />\n女人應該扮唔知 男人識番屋企就得 <br />\n但女人偷食就十惡不赦 <br />\n根本所有男人都係狗</blockquote><br />\n偷食同叫雞點撚同"},{"pid":"11e65d1c175193d2582e886f9427d0e4e1b0f9e0","tid":213200,"uid":68370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"仲唔篤爆佢地等幾時?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}